response.original_title: Sinatra: An Unauthorized Biography of the Legend
response.overview: This fascinating biography of the lengendary "Blue Eyes" takes us on an informative and captivating excursion through his life and career. From his fledgling days to present stardom, his career is chronicled in infinite detail, including rare and never before seen footage.
response.title: Sinatra: An Unauthorized Biography of the Legend
